{
  "episode_id": "2026-06-20",
  "chunks": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "听众朋友们大家好，欢迎收听AI每日先锋，今天是2026年6月20日。我是主持人晓晓。",
      "start": 1.0,
      "duration": 9.404,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_001_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_001_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "大家好，我是博文。",
      "start": 10.853,
      "duration": 1.393,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_002_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_002_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哎博文，你今天刷新闻了吗？我感觉今天科技圈有两个事特别炸——呃不是，我是说，特别有看头。",
      "start": 12.743,
      "duration": 7.488,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_003_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_003_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哈哈晓晓，你刚才那口误挺真实的。哪两个事？",
      "start": 20.684,
      "duration": 3.439,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_004_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_004_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "一个是AI全自动做药，另一个是人形机器人突然有了\"通用小脑\"。我就在想啊，今天的AI好像同时在两件事上发力——一边是创造力的爆发，从写代码到造分子；另一边是对自己能力边界的反思。这两个方向同时迎来临界点，太有意思了。",
      "start": 24.528,
      "duration": 23.617,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_005_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_005_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "你这个总结挺到位的。一个往外走，一个往内看，确实是今天AI圈特别有意思的张力。那咱们就先聊聊AI做药这个？",
      "start": 48.578,
      "duration": 8.795,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_006_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_006_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "好嘞！博文，我今天早上看到这条新闻的时候真的愣了一下——说GPT系列的相关AI，在药物研发上做出了\"原创新成果\"，而且是从靶点发现到分子设计，端到端搞定的。",
      "start": 57.838,
      "duration": 15.63,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_007_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_007_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这个\"端到端\"是关键。晓晓，你给听众翻译翻译？",
      "start": 73.93,
      "duration": 3.875,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_008_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_008_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "等的就是你这句话！简单说，以前的AI在制药里基本就是个\"超级实习生\"的角色——你给它一个靶点，它帮你筛一堆分子，然后人类科学家再挑、再改、再验证。但这次不一样，它是从头到尾自己把链条跑通了。",
      "start": 78.256,
      "duration": 16.825,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_009_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_009_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对，这就有点\"从助手变成作者\"的味道了。而且我注意到这次特别强调\"原创\"两个字。",
      "start": 95.581,
      "duration": 6.966,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_010_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_010_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对！\"原创\"这两个字我盯了半天。博文，这意味着什么？",
      "start": 102.985,
      "duration": 5.181,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_011_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_011_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "意味着AI不只是把已有的分子数据库重新排列组合，它生成的结构可能是人类专家从来没想过的。这种\"非显而易见性\"才是真正的科学价值。",
      "start": 108.627,
      "duration": 12.365,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_012_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_012_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哇，这个厉害了。那对我们普通人意味着什么？是不是以后新药会便宜很多？",
      "start": 121.437,
      "duration": 5.137,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_013_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_013_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "理性地说，药物价格是个复杂系统，但研发周期确实有望被压缩。传统一款新药要十多年、几十亿美元，如果AI能把前期探索阶段砍掉一半，整个行业的资金效率会质变。",
      "start": 127.048,
      "duration": 15.064,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_014_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_014_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "我来打个比方啊，这就好像以前开饭店，每道菜都得从种菜开始；现在突然有了一个中央厨房，你只要告诉它要什么味道的菜，它自己研究菜谱、自己种菜、自己炒。",
      "start": 142.539,
      "duration": 15.151,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_015_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_015_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哈哈哈这个比喻可以，不过晓晓，背后的算力和数据壁垒其实非常高，不是所有团队都能玩的。",
      "start": 158.154,
      "duration": 7.619,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_016_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_016_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对，这个我懂——大厂游戏嘛。那博文，咱们换个话题，我今天看到的另一条新闻也让我很激动——全球第一个\"人形机器人通用小脑\"模型出来了，训练数据用了整整2万小时的人类动作。",
      "start": 166.19,
      "duration": 16.215,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_017_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_017_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这个我仔细看了。2万小时这个数字很关键。",
      "start": 182.841,
      "duration": 3.57,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_018_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_018_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "关键在哪？",
      "start": 186.828,
      "duration": 0.914,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_019_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_019_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "关键在于它是\"零样本泛化\"。你不需要为每个新任务重新训练，模型看到新场景就能直接上手。",
      "start": 188.238,
      "duration": 8.446,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_020_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_020_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "等等博文，\"零样本泛化\"听起来好专业，你给翻译翻译？",
      "start": 197.096,
      "duration": 5.616,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_021_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_021_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "简单说，就是你不用教它一万次，它看一次就能做。这跟我们以前那种\"一招鲜\"的机器人完全不一样。",
      "start": 203.191,
      "duration": 6.618,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_022_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_022_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哦！这不就是机器人的\"GPT时刻\"嘛！就像我侄子，看过我做一次蛋糕，他下次就能自己试着做，虽然做得不好，但那个\"举一反三\"的能力是有了。",
      "start": 210.241,
      "duration": 12.06,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_023_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_023_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "你这个比喻非常恰当，本质就是从\"专用控制器\"走向\"通用智能底座\"。以前每个动作都要写代码，现在有了\"通用小脑\"，上层应用开发会爆发。",
      "start": 222.769,
      "duration": 12.974,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_024_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_024_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对！我突然想到，这其实跟AI做药有点像——都是从一个\"专用工具\"升级成一个\"通用底座\"，然后整个生态就起来了。",
      "start": 236.233,
      "duration": 11.494,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_025_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_025_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "没错，这就是范式跃迁。晓晓你这产品经理的直觉确实灵敏。",
      "start": 248.204,
      "duration": 5.224,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_026_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_026_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哈哈谢谢夸奖！那接下来轻松一点，我最近还刷到几个挺有意思的学术动向。博文你最近看arXiv了吗？",
      "start": 253.846,
      "duration": 8.272,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_027_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_027_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "看了，有几个我也想聊。",
      "start": 262.557,
      "duration": 1.785,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_028_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_028_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "先说一个我特别好奇的——有篇论文在研究\"扩散语言模型\"。博文，这个方向你觉得靠谱吗？",
      "start": 264.754,
      "duration": 8.403,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_029_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_029_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "挺有意思的尝试。现在所有的大模型都是\"自回归\"，一个字一个字往外蹦，扩散模型在图像里是整体生成的，有人就想了，能不能把这套机制搬到语言上。",
      "start": 273.65,
      "duration": 12.016,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_030_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_030_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "那这不就是\"换一条路走路\"嘛？",
      "start": 286.075,
      "duration": 2.612,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_031_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_031_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哈哈可以这么理解。具体效果还得观察，但它至少说明一件事——Transformer加自回归这套组合，不一定是终极答案。",
      "start": 289.174,
      "duration": 9.012,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_032_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_032_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "行，这条先存着。哎还有一个让我有点担心的事——有研究说LLM存在\"认知盲区\"，特别是在临床表格数据上，会出现\"不知道自己不知道\"的情况。",
      "start": 298.628,
      "duration": 14.629,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_033_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_033_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这个挺重要的。它是用\"跨模型归因分歧\"的方法来检测的——就是让好几个模型同时看同一个问题，看它们哪里意见不一致。",
      "start": 313.717,
      "duration": 9.361,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_034_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_034_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哦，原来是这样！那\"不知道自己不知道\"具体是啥意思？",
      "start": 323.549,
      "duration": 4.571,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_035_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_035_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "通俗讲，就是模型胡说八道的时候还特别自信。在闲聊里问题不大，但在医疗、法律这种场景，是会出人命的。",
      "start": 328.532,
      "duration": 9.404,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_036_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_036_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对！这种\"不知道自己不知道\"比\"知道但说错\"更可怕。",
      "start": 338.381,
      "duration": 4.659,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_037_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_037_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "是的，所以这类研究越来越重要，是AI安全落地的关键拼图。",
      "start": 343.495,
      "duration": 5.399,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_038_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_038_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "好，最后再聊一个\"十年回顾\"——有篇综述系统梳理了过去十年AI for SE和SE for AI的演进。博文，你怎么评价这十年？",
      "start": 349.334,
      "duration": 12.19,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_039_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_039_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我觉得这十年最核心的变化是——AI从\"软件工程的工具\"变成了\"软件工程的主体\"。以前我们用AI写代码辅助，现在是AI自己写、自己测、自己改。",
      "start": 362.002,
      "duration": 12.234,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_040_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_040_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哇，那\"开发者\"这个职业会不会消失？",
      "start": 374.717,
      "duration": 3.396,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_041_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_041_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
